flow
  orient(agent)
  -> context(flow_spec, architecture)
  -> consensus(blocking | pending)
  -> report(status)


shape
  CONCEPT: BRIEF
  CENTROID
    rapid loading of development context
  AXES
    historical <-> current
    technical <-> social
    blocking <-> open
  SATELLITES
    accord (what is blocked)
    flow-spec (how we write)
    arch-diagram (where we are)
  VOID
    not debugging
    not history log
    not unrelated data
  TEXTURE
    calibrating the compass


